flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Parts order creation, urgent request, inventory imbalance, core return initiation.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve parts orders and urgent requests from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze inventory levels and order details using Cortex Auto Forecast.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder - Determine expedited shipping options and cross-DC transfers.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Execute optimized fulfillment and transfer decisions.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Cortex Monitoring - Monitor and adjust decisions based on real-time data.]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital, minimized stockouts, improved on-time in-full (OTIF) delivery rates.]
  N3 -->|Insufficient inventory for urgent req...| B1[Expedite shipping and reallocate inventory.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Minimized delays and ensured on-time delivery.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|High holding costs in certain DCs.| B2[Initiate cross-DC transfers.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Balanced inventory levels and reduced holding costs.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Excess core returns.| B3[Allocate cores to remanufacturing programs.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Optimized working capital and throughput.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]